title: Reflexology A Way to Better Health Nicola M Hall DVDRip MP4
description:
Reflexology is a form of complementary medicine that uses precise forms of massage to reflex areas found in the feet. These areas correspond to all parts of the body and it is possible to treat many different disorders using this treatment.

This demonstration of a reflexology treatment is given by Nicola M Hall, Director of the Bayly School of Reflexology. Nicola shows how to apply reflexology massage to all the reflex areas in the feet using the method taught by The Bayly School of Reflexology.
